(NARRATOR) <i>As the three-way</i>
 <i>battle between the two squads</i>
 <i>and Martian Terraformars...</i>

00:00:12.745 --> 00:00:18.551 position:16% line:77% align:start
 <i>rages on, Hong continues</i>
 <i>to release her deadly</i>
 <i>bacteria to protect Annex 1...</i>

00:00:18.585 --> 00:00:19.519 position:24% line:89% align:start
Everyone, retreat!

00:00:20.553 --> 00:00:21.020 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>...forcing Squad 3 to fall </i>
 <i>back.</i>

00:00:22.856 --> 00:00:26.861 position:16% line:77% align:start
 <i>Meanwhile, Alexander has</i>
 <i>launched a suicidal attack</i>
 <i>within the walls of the Annex...</i>

00:00:26.894 --> 00:00:31.531 position:16% line:77% align:start
 <i>1 in a last-ditch effort</i>
 <i>to save his true love back on</i>
 <i>earth.</i>

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:36.704 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>His drastic move has left Squad</i>
 <i>4 with heavy casualties.</i>

00:00:50.118 --> 00:00:50.951 position:30% line:89% align:start
(LIU) Hong...

00:00:50.986 --> 00:00:52.120 position:33% line:89% align:start
[gasp] Yes?

00:00:53.955 --> 00:00:56.124 position:5% line:77% align:start
Once we're done treating Xi and
the other infected members of
the team, we'll hunt for the...

00:00:56.157 --> 00:00:58.525 position:10% line:89% align:start
Second Squad. You stay here.

00:00:58.559 --> 00:01:00.427 position:7% line:83% align:start
There are pleanty of supplies
and food.

00:01:02.063 --> 00:01:05.567 position:5% line:77% align:start
Continue releasing bacteria for
as long as you can. But don't
burn yourself out.

00:01:05.967 --> 00:01:09.905 position:5% line:83% align:start
O-okay. Yes, I'll... do what you
said.

00:01:10.672 --> 00:01:11.439 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:01:13.175 --> 00:01:16.678 position:10% line:77% align:start
Hey, what's up with that sad
face? I wanna make sure you're
not getting any guilty...

00:01:16.711 --> 00:01:18.747 position:7% line:83% align:start
feelings in that pretty ittle
head of yours.

00:01:18.948 --> 00:01:19.115 position:83% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:01:20.383 --> 00:01:23.585 position:5% line:83% align:start
You did everything you could to
protect all of us, and Annex 1.

00:01:23.920 --> 00:01:29.659 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>So now we'll do everything we</i>
 <i>can to protect you. We're a</i>
 <i>unit. That's all there is to it.</i>

00:01:29.692 --> 00:01:30.526 position:35% line:89% align:start
[sipping]

00:01:31.727 --> 00:01:33.095 position:5% line:83% align:start
(LIU) <i>It will take time to treat</i>
 <i>the injured...</i>

00:01:34.096 --> 00:01:35.464 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>This shouldn't have happened.</i>

00:01:37.533 --> 00:01:40.136 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>The first and second were cut</i>
 <i>off from Captain Komachi. I</i>
 <i>hope the roaches haven't...</i>

00:01:40.170 --> 00:01:43.106 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>split them up and captured</i>
 <i>them. Or worse...</i>

00:01:44.740 --> 00:01:47.010 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Put me in contact with Squads 1</i>
 <i>and 2.</i>

00:01:47.044 --> 00:01:47.777 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yes, sir.

00:01:54.718 --> 00:01:57.621 position:13% line:89% align:start
06. WEAPONS AND TECHNIQUES

00:03:32.353 --> 00:03:37.925 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>This is commander Liu Yiwi. I</i>
 <i>order you to hand over the First</i>
 <i>and Second. Or I'll destroy...</i>

00:03:37.958 --> 00:03:39.126 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>you with a missle attack.</i>

00:03:39.160 --> 00:03:39.894 position:5% line:89% align:start
Uh...

00:03:43.230 --> 00:03:47.234 position:10% line:5% align:start
Michelle, tell that scum you
won't take his shit. He betrayed
the mission.

00:03:48.803 --> 00:03:53.308 position:7% line:77% align:start
They must have had some secret
plan all along. That's why
they're after both of us. How...

00:03:53.341 --> 00:03:54.909 position:7% line:89% align:start
can you be so calm right now?

00:03:55.377 --> 00:03:56.744 position:19% line:89% align:start
It's called "resolve."

00:03:57.078 --> 00:03:57.978 position:5% line:89% align:start
(AKARI) [grunt]

00:03:58.846 --> 00:04:00.282 position:19% line:83% align:start
Squad 4's plans don't
matter to me.

00:04:01.882 --> 00:04:04.886 position:5% line:5% align:start
I knew what I needed to do when
I came to Mars and nothing's
going to stop me.

00:04:05.686 --> 00:04:06.620 position:24% line:89% align:start
You're not alone.

00:04:08.924 --> 00:04:10.759 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>I have promises to keep too...</i>

00:04:13.428 --> 00:04:14.262 position:27% line:89% align:start
[pained grunts]

00:04:15.297 --> 00:04:16.098 position:35% line:89% align:start
What now?!

00:04:19.302 --> 00:04:20.269 position:55% line:89% align:start
What happened?

00:04:20.702 --> 00:04:21.937 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's... over there!

00:04:43.292 --> 00:04:44.293 position:5% line:89% align:start
(DONATELLO) <i>Michelle.</i>

00:04:48.798 --> 00:04:49.799 position:27% line:89% align:start
What do you see?

00:05:13.957 --> 00:05:15.159 position:21% line:5% align:start
Just like my father!

00:05:27.772 --> 00:05:28.139 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:05:28.873 --> 00:05:30.708 position:5% line:83% align:start
Welcome back, sir. We missed
you.

00:05:31.876 --> 00:05:34.179 position:5% line:5% align:start
[sigh] It's bad... Captain...

00:05:34.513 --> 00:05:37.682 position:10% line:5% align:start
We acted irresponsibly. For
that, I am sorry.

00:05:38.149 --> 00:05:43.422 position:10% line:77% align:start
You better be sorry. But the
other squads weren't any better.
And, you saved my life when I...

00:05:43.455 --> 00:05:44.756 position:10% line:89% align:start
could have died back there.

00:05:44.789 --> 00:05:45.690 position:30% line:89% align:start
So thank you.

00:05:46.758 --> 00:05:48.427 position:10% line:89% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>Is this everyone?</i>

00:05:48.460 --> 00:05:50.996 position:5% line:89% align:start
(SYLVESTER) <i>Yes. My son is dead.</i>

00:05:54.900 --> 00:06:01.207 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>That damn fool! I don't care</i>
 <i>how frustrated he might have</i>
 <i>been, How close we were to...</i>

00:06:01.240 --> 00:06:05.378 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>capturing the facility. Or how</i>
 <i>impossible the situation may</i>
 <i>have been...</i>

00:06:05.878 --> 00:06:08.080 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>Dying was against orders!</i>

00:06:09.148 --> 00:06:10.217 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:06:16.022 --> 00:06:16.889 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>Now...</i>

00:06:17.557 --> 00:06:23.897 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:06:25.999 --> 00:06:30.403 position:7% line:77% align:start
I promise you: Earth will get
a vaccine, even if I have to
give my life for it.

00:06:32.138 --> 00:06:33.240 position:27% line:89% align:start
Look, captain...

00:06:34.575 --> 00:06:36.743 position:13% line:77% align:start
I'll tell you all I know,
and the challenges that lie
ahead.

00:06:38.246 --> 00:06:41.415 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>A bacteria-type M.O. operation</i>
 <i>must have been performed on that</i>
 <i>girl.</i>

00:06:42.049 --> 00:06:45.086 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>There's a good chance that tech</i>
 <i>is exclusive to China.</i>

00:06:45.519 --> 00:06:47.955 position:5% line:83% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>Are you saying shes a</i>
 <i>human bioweapon?</i>

00:06:49.924 --> 00:06:53.027 position:5% line:77% align:start
(SYLVESTER) <i>Yes. If she can get</i>
 <i>close to her target, she can</i>
 <i>carry out assassinations or...</i>

00:06:53.060 --> 00:06:54.161 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>terrorist attacks.</i>

00:06:56.063 --> 00:06:58.500 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>It seems the rest of them have</i>
 <i>undergone a type of</i>
 <i>metamorphosis operation...</i>

00:06:58.533 --> 00:06:59.934 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>quite different from ours.</i>

00:07:01.936 --> 00:07:04.339 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>Even in their human form, they</i>
 <i>had strength and powers that</i>
 <i>nearly matched those of their...</i>

00:07:04.373 --> 00:07:05.440 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>animal-hybrid states.</i>

00:07:06.941 --> 00:07:10.946 position:7% line:5% align:start
Which means... they can't just
revert and lead
normal lives, like we can.

00:07:11.446 --> 00:07:16.451 position:19% line:77% align:start
 <i>One night in the same</i>
 <i>room as that bacteria-type girl</i>
 <i>would poison the average human.</i>

00:07:16.952 --> 00:07:22.124 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>Their sharpened senses would</i>
 <i>make normal olfactory and</i>
 <i>auditory stimuli almost...</i>

00:07:22.157 --> 00:07:22.891 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>unbearable.</i>

00:07:23.693 --> 00:07:25.260 position:16% line:83% align:start
Then does that mean that
they're...

00:07:25.294 --> 00:07:25.994 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mm-hm.

00:07:27.530 --> 00:07:30.300 position:7% line:5% align:start
To gain those powers, they've
abandoned the one hope we still
cling to...

00:07:30.566 --> 00:07:33.835 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Never again will they be able to</i>
 <i>live an ordinary life.</i>

00:07:34.504 --> 00:07:36.472 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>They're killing machines now.</i>

00:07:38.274 --> 00:07:41.044 position:5% line:77% align:start
And with that kind of sacrifice,
they have nothing left to lose.
They don't care about the...

00:07:41.077 --> 00:07:42.145 position:19% line:89% align:start
other squads on Mars.

00:07:43.913 --> 00:07:46.382 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(KANAKO) But I can't understand,</i>
 <i>why do they want Michelle and</i>
 <i>Akari so badly?</i>

00:07:46.416 --> 00:07:47.317 position:5% line:89% align:start
(SYLVESTER) <i>I think I know...</i>

00:07:48.451 --> 00:07:51.321 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Both of them was born with</i>
 <i>prized Mosaic Organs.</i>

00:07:51.622 --> 00:07:57.528 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>Officer Davis is a medical</i>
 <i>miracle. Unlike the rest of us,</i>
 <i>she wasn't an experiment made...</i>

00:07:57.561 --> 00:07:58.329 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>in a lab.</i>

00:08:00.230 --> 00:08:04.802 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>But Akari Hizamaru was wholly</i>
 <i>engineered. He owes his</i>
 <i>existance completely to science.</i>

00:08:05.169 --> 00:08:08.839 position:21% line:77% align:start
 <i>A way to make the</i>
 <i>Mosaic Organs hereditary does</i>
 <i>exist.</i>

00:08:09.173 --> 00:08:14.044 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>The promise of genetically</i>
 <i>transferring moasaic organs</i>
 <i>could empower a single nation...</i>

00:08:14.078 --> 00:08:16.213 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>with a master race of soldiers.</i>

00:08:16.246 --> 00:08:20.452 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>An army of crustacean</i>
 <i>commandos! A</i>
 <i>batallion of electricity...</i>

00:08:20.485 --> 00:08:21.852 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>weilding spies.</i>

00:08:23.187 --> 00:08:24.922 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>You could make politicians</i>
 <i>impervious to an assassin's</i>
 <i>poison.</i>

00:08:26.857 --> 00:08:31.496 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>The medical applications would</i>
 <i>be endless. Monopolizing the</i>
 <i>technology would generate...</i>

00:08:31.529 --> 00:08:32.863 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>incredible wealth.</i>

00:08:34.632 --> 00:08:38.536 position:5% line:5% align:start
Any country possessing it would
rise to immense power! That's
what Liu's squad is after.

00:08:44.075 --> 00:08:48.614 position:7% line:77% align:start
Then we have our new job: Save
Akari and Michelle... Stop squad
4.

00:08:48.647 --> 00:08:49.548 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yes, sir!

00:08:49.582 --> 00:08:51.049 position:5% line:89% align:start
Roger that, Captain.

00:08:52.951 --> 00:08:57.390 position:5% line:77% align:start
(SYLVESTER) <i>But we can't forget:</i>
 <i>It's not just Squad 4 that wants</i>
 <i>them. We need to hurry.</i>

00:09:05.231 --> 00:09:07.233 position:35% line:89% align:start
Ji...Jooo.

00:09:12.304 --> 00:09:16.242 position:19% line:77% align:start
Sorry but I've got you
wrapped up, bullet ant. You're a
paraponera, right?

00:09:18.578 --> 00:09:23.916 position:16% line:77% align:start
My bagworm silk is thin, but
it's strong. Now put down my
ship.

00:09:24.718 --> 00:09:26.086 position:38% line:89% align:start
Jooo...

00:09:30.424 --> 00:09:34.928 position:13% line:77% align:start
Don't put up a fight. You
just let me take you down nice
and easy.

00:09:40.333 --> 00:09:41.134 position:33% line:89% align:start
[struggling]

00:09:43.738 --> 00:09:45.440 position:38% line:89% align:start
Jooo...

00:09:53.281 --> 00:09:58.619 position:7% line:77% align:start
Do I seem familiar to you? We
share the same strength. From my
father.

00:09:59.620 --> 00:10:04.225 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>What's wrong, Akari? Did you</i>
 <i>think I'd lose my cool when</i>
 <i>faced with the creature that...</i>

00:10:04.258 --> 00:10:04.992 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>killed him?</i>

00:10:06.994 --> 00:10:09.631 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>I appreciate the concern. But</i>
 <i>I've been ready for this ever</i>
 <i>since I learned the...</i>

00:10:09.665 --> 00:10:11.966 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>terraformars could steal</i>
 <i>our abilities.</i>

00:10:12.768 --> 00:10:16.472 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm as calm as can be. I'm also
cranky as hell!

00:10:17.673 --> 00:10:20.309 position:27% line:89% align:start
[pushing grunts]

00:10:21.143 --> 00:10:22.478 position:41% line:89% align:start
Akari!

00:10:22.711 --> 00:10:23.579 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right!

00:10:26.048 --> 00:10:26.415 position:27% line:89% align:start
[pulling grunts]

00:10:30.219 --> 00:10:31.520 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scream]

00:10:34.424 --> 00:10:36.992 position:38% line:89% align:start
Jooiii.

00:10:37.527 --> 00:10:39.729 position:13% line:83% align:start
You thought you'd come and
capture us?

00:10:39.762 --> 00:10:41.664 position:10% line:89% align:start
Okay, Michelle. Let's do it!

00:10:44.067 --> 00:10:45.668 position:7% line:5% align:start
(DONATELLO) <i>Were you here the</i>
 <i>whole time, Michelle?</i>

00:10:47.070 --> 00:10:49.706 position:5% line:83% align:start
Tell me, dear. What do you think
of those ants?

00:10:51.107 --> 00:10:53.042 position:21% line:89% align:start
Mmm... They're okay.

00:10:54.745 --> 00:10:58.481 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>Your arms look like my fathers'.</i>
 <i>But I won't let that resemblance</i>
 <i>cloud my judgement.</i>

00:10:58.515 --> 00:11:02.419 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>So long as you stay away from my</i>
 <i>friends, I'm happy.</i>

00:11:02.453 --> 00:11:05.589 position:10% line:83% align:start
But because you're a shitty
roach, I'm stamping you out.

00:11:10.594 --> 00:11:11.362 position:27% line:89% align:start
[yanking grunt]

00:11:16.133 --> 00:11:17.067 position:27% line:89% align:start
[punching grunt]

00:11:18.636 --> 00:11:19.069 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:11:20.571 --> 00:11:21.205 position:27% line:89% align:start
[punching grunt]

00:11:22.573 --> 00:11:26.210 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>I can feel each punch vibrate</i>
 <i>through the silk. Incredible...</i>

00:11:26.410 --> 00:11:30.080 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>She's steeled herself for this</i>
 <i>all week. She's so calm!</i>

00:11:30.849 --> 00:11:36.053 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>If she holds no grudge with that</i>
 <i>monster for what he did? Then</i>
 <i>why the crazy hard punches?!</i>

00:11:36.688 --> 00:11:39.524 position:5% line:89% align:start
But did you know this, Michelle?

00:11:40.158 --> 00:11:41.626 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>Of all the insects...</i>

00:11:41.660 --> 00:11:43.395 position:10% line:83% align:start
(MICHELLE) This is where you
die.

00:11:43.628 --> 00:11:44.563 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:11:45.664 --> 00:11:47.232 position:10% line:5% align:start
(DONATELLO) <i>Ants are unique</i>
 <i>creatures.</i>

00:11:47.532 --> 00:11:50.101 position:13% line:83% align:start
Now! This is our chance to
finish him!

00:11:50.502 --> 00:11:52.572 position:16% line:89% align:start
(AKARI) <i>Michelle! Do it!</i>

00:11:53.806 --> 00:11:55.073 position:16% line:89% align:start
(DONATELLO) <i>Ants are...</i>

00:11:55.908 --> 00:11:56.576 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:12:03.416 --> 00:12:04.082 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:12:06.786 --> 00:12:08.554 position:7% line:89% align:start
(DONATELLO) <i>...the strongest.</i>

00:12:08.588 --> 00:12:09.422 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:12:11.257 --> 00:12:13.259 position:10% line:83% align:start
(DONATELLO) <i>The strongest by</i>
 <i>far.</i>

00:12:14.193 --> 00:12:15.696 position:38% line:89% align:start
Ji Joooi

00:12:16.228 --> 00:12:16.763 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:12:17.698 --> 00:12:19.265 position:5% line:5% align:start
He should be feeling the effects
by now...

00:12:21.068 --> 00:12:23.604 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>Didn't Michelle's explosive</i>
 <i>fluid penetrate that thing's</i>
 <i>internal organs?</i>

00:12:38.752 --> 00:12:39.453 position:41% line:89% align:start
Shit.

00:12:42.489 --> 00:12:48.896 position:35% line:89% align:start
Joooij...

00:12:48.930 --> 00:12:50.130 position:13% line:89% align:start
(AKARI) <i>What's the matter?</i>

00:12:52.867 --> 00:12:54.802 position:13% line:89% align:start
Can't break out, can you?

00:12:55.269 --> 00:12:58.473 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Sorry, but I'm not a brute-force</i>
 <i>type like Michelle!</i>

00:12:58.740 --> 00:13:03.478 position:10% line:77% align:start
My style's more tie-you-up,
weigh-you-down, and bury you
underground.

00:13:05.346 --> 00:13:08.316 position:35% line:89% align:start
[inhaling]

00:13:09.450 --> 00:13:15.724 position:16% line:89% align:start
Joo jooj. J-jooo, jiii.

00:13:15.758 --> 00:13:16.324 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:13:21.630 --> 00:13:22.331 position:5% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:13:22.998 --> 00:13:24.333 position:5% line:89% align:start
The silk!

00:13:25.467 --> 00:13:26.201 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:13:44.353 --> 00:13:45.354 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:13:53.296 --> 00:13:58.702 position:5% line:83% align:start
[chuckle] What's up? You want me
too, new guy? Or these threads?

00:13:58.969 --> 00:14:03.941 position:10% line:77% align:start
But you know something, red
ant? I wouldn't be too
confident of my chances if I...

00:14:03.974 --> 00:14:04.709 position:35% line:89% align:start
were you.

