[exhaling]

00:15:04.637 --> 00:15:06.005 position:33% line:89% align:start
Jo jio ji...

00:15:07.339 --> 00:15:08.775 position:24% line:89% align:start
Ji, jiii, joiii...

00:15:15.115 --> 00:15:15.648 position:38% line:89% align:start
[quiver]

