00:15:26.860 --> 00:15:28.294 position:55% line:89% align:start
Let's do this!

00:15:32.132 --> 00:15:35.301 position:52% line:89% align:start
[pained grunts]

00:15:37.004 --> 00:15:41.809 position:16% line:77% align:start
