00:16:28.991 --> 00:16:29.692 position:75% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:16:35.064 --> 00:16:37.533 position:7% line:89% align:start
And the first point... is mine!

00:16:42.873 --> 00:16:44.373 position:19% line:5% align:start
 <i>These things feel no pain!</i>

00:16:44.975 --> 00:16:45.708 position:5% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:16:47.043 --> 00:16:48.544 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:16:55.185 --> 00:16:57.621 position:21% line:89% align:start
[grunts and groans]

00:16:57.654 --> 00:16:58.388 position:16% line:89% align:start
[struggling for breath]

00:17:00.324 --> 00:17:05.528 position:19% line:5% align:start
 <i>He wasn't afraid... to</i>
