 <i>to do whatever it takes... to...</i>

00:17:05.562 --> 00:17:06.163 position:44% line:5% align:start
 <i>win.</i>

00:17:06.197 --> 00:17:07.731 position:30% line:89% align:start
[pained grunt]

00:17:11.802 --> 00:17:16.807 position:5% line:77% align:start
(YAEKO) <i>They shot him! They shot</i>
 <i>Hizamaru! I don't know if he's</i>
 <i>alive but at this rate, the...</i>

00:17:16.841 --> 00:17:19.644 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>roaches will take Akari! Do you</i>
 <i>copy?</i>

00:17:19.677 --> 00:17:21.412 position:21% line:83% align:start
Incoming transmission from
Vehicle 2.

00:17:23.481 --> 00:17:25.483 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>Then you won't be able to</i>
 <i>collect his body. Think about</i>
 <i>it: that's worse than Akari...</i>

00:17:25.516 --> 00:17:26.584 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>just dying, right?</i>

00:17:28.387 --> 00:17:32.257 position:5% line:77% align:start
Thanks to him, we've got missles
pointed at us. We've had to
drive like mad men all over...

00:17:32.291 --> 00:17:32.924 position:35% line:89% align:start
the place.

00:17:33.824 --> 00:17:36.427 position:7% line:83% align:start
I can't take it anymore. Just
shoot!

00:17:36.862 --> 00:17:41.199 position:13% line:77% align:start
Hizamaru and Michelle are
battling the roaches. Right now
they're between vehicles 1...

00:17:41.233 --> 00:17:41.934 position:41% line:89% align:start
and 2.

00:17:43.201 --> 00:17:46.505 position:5% line:83% align:start
Please don't wait, fire on both
of them and the terraformars.

00:17:46.538 --> 00:17:49.942 position:7% line:83% align:start
Do whatever you have to! I beg
you, just make sure I survive!

00:17:50.208 --> 00:17:55.514 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>Hurry! I'm scared that the</i>
 <i>roaches will ccome for me next!</i>
 <i>I know they will! I don't...</i>

00:17:55.547 --> 00:17:56.949 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>want to die! Save me!</i>

00:17:57.150 --> 00:17:58.850 position:5% line:89% align:start
So Rank 98 is betraying them.

00:17:59.785 --> 00:18:04.456 position:7% line:77% align:start
Typical non-combatant. It was
only a matter of time before she
broke under the pressure.

00:18:04.756 --> 00:18:07.526 position:5% line:83% align:start
The target she provided is
confirmed and accurate.

00:18:07.559 --> 00:18:07.961 position:78% line:89% align:start
Do it.

00:18:16.669 --> 00:18:17.470 position:58% line:89% align:start
(BAO) <i>Firing!</i>

00:18:22.542 --> 00:18:26.546 position:7% line:77% align:start
(MICHELLE) <i>Squad 4 is worried </i>
  <i>that Akari and I will be taken</i>
 <i>by the terraformars before...</i>

00:18:26.579 --> 00:18:30.884 position:16% line:77% align:start
 <i>they can recover our bodies</i>
 <i>themselves. Plus, they want</i>
 <i>to prevent squads 1 and...</i>

00:18:30.918 --> 00:18:33.486 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>2 from connecting with Joseph</i>
 <i>to launch an attack. </i>

00:18:33.954 --> 00:18:34.487 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mhm.

00:18:36.290 --> 00:18:39.193 position:10% line:77% align:start
(MICHELLE) <i>We can't use our</i>
 <i>radios, so we'll use a</i>
 <i>smoke signal to alert Squad 6...</i>

00:18:39.226 --> 00:18:40.160 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>that we need help.</i>

00:18:41.328 --> 00:18:44.932 position:10% line:83% align:start
To get them to launch the
missle. Pretend to betray us.

00:18:44.965 --> 00:18:46.900 position:10% line:89% align:start
Understood. I'll do my best.

00:18:46.934 --> 00:18:47.668 position:50% line:89% align:start
You'll be great!

00:18:49.703 --> 00:18:53.141 position:19% line:77% align:start
(MICHELLE) <i>If I get into</i>
 <i>trouble, follow the plan! Got</i>
 <i>it? We'll outsmart Squad 4...</i>

00:18:53.174 --> 00:18:54.842 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>and make them waste a missle.</i>

00:18:55.176 --> 00:18:55.809 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right!

00:18:59.214 --> 00:19:01.682 position:7% line:89% align:start
It's in your hands now, Alex!

00:19:03.018 --> 00:19:04.518 position:7% line:89% align:start
(ALEX) <i>Leave it to me, Yaeko.</i>

00:19:06.121 --> 00:19:09.024 position:7% line:77% align:start
I'll bring the missle down off
traget. And send the smoke
signal into the sky!

00:19:20.302 --> 00:19:21.703 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:19:22.038 --> 00:19:22.704 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:19:30.913 --> 00:19:31.714 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:19:34.350 --> 00:19:34.884 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:19:37.286 --> 00:19:39.055 position:10% line:83% align:start
[gasp] I'm gonna haunt your
dreams!

00:19:43.893 --> 00:19:44.727 position:41% line:89% align:start
Huh?!

00:19:45.061 --> 00:19:46.896 position:24% line:89% align:start
It...didn't work?

00:19:52.002 --> 00:19:57.240 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>We wasted their missle, but we</i>
 <i>didn't get our smoke signal. The</i>
 <i>plan failed.</i>

00:20:00.844 --> 00:20:02.245 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:20:06.950 --> 00:20:08.319 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'll load a second one.

00:20:08.352 --> 00:20:08.919 position:5% line:89% align:start
Wait!

00:20:10.020 --> 00:20:12.923 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>It went off course and missed</i>
 <i>the target. Why?</i>

00:20:17.761 --> 00:20:20.098 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>Rank 7? Could he have rigged the</i>
 <i>missle?</i>

00:20:22.233 --> 00:20:26.771 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>(NARRATOR) As a strategy,</i>
 <i>Michelle and her team's plan was</i>
 <i>incredibly risky...</i>

00:20:28.372 --> 00:20:30.942 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>(MICHELLE) If Liu hadn't taken</i>
 <i>the bait and fired the missle...</i>

00:20:32.043 --> 00:20:35.780 position:10% line:5% align:start
 <i>If nothing had disrupted the</i>
 <i>missle and it hit vehicle 2 with</i>
 <i>Yaeko in it...</i>

00:20:36.381 --> 00:20:39.284 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>Or, if the missle had detonated</i>
 <i>anywhere near us...</i>

00:20:40.219 --> 00:20:45.023 position:7% line:77% align:start
(NARRATOR) <i>It was the slimmest</i>
 <i>of hopes... a hope that was on</i>
 <i>the verge of disappearing any...</i>

00:20:45.057 --> 00:20:45.790 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>moment!</i>

00:20:47.793 --> 00:20:49.328 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>But it worked...</i>

00:20:50.129 --> 00:20:52.131 position:19% line:89% align:start
