00:20:54.433 --> 00:20:57.803 position:5% line:83% align:start
(NARRATOR) <i>A fallen comrade from</i>
 <i>another land had intervened!</i>

00:20:59.838 --> 00:21:01.173 position:10% line:83% align:start
(AKARI) <i>As long as I've got</i>
 <i>this...</i>

00:21:01.407 --> 00:21:04.143 position:19% line:89% align:start
Then the fight is on!

00:21:06.879 --> 00:21:11.317 position:10% line:5% align:start
 <i>So Rank 7 knew... theat we'd</i>
 <i>fire without hesitation if we</i>
 <i>had to.</i>

00:21:12.784 --> 00:21:17.991 position:10% line:5% align:start
 <i>He destroyed the launcher to</i>
 <i>make us think the missles were</i>
 <i>still usable! He tricked us!</i>

00:21:19.359 --> 00:21:23.029 position:16% line:5% align:start
 <i>He must have removed the</i>
 <i>explosive warhead and replaced</i>
 <i>it with something that...</i>

00:21:23.062 --> 00:21:24.831 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>changed the missle's center of</i>
 <i>gravity.</i>

00:21:26.032 --> 00:21:28.335 position:10% line:5% align:start
 <i>So... the weapon he planted</i>
 <i>inside was..!</i>

00:21:30.036 --> 00:21:34.175 position:5% line:5% align:start
(AKARI) <i>I don't know who you are</i>
 <i>but our hopes are joined as one!</i>

00:21:35.742 --> 00:21:38.845 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>You gave me something that only</i>
 <i>I can locate, with my moth</i>
 <i>powers...</i>

00:21:39.846 --> 00:21:45.920 position:13% line:77% align:start
(NARRATOR) <i>In sacrificing</i>
 <i>himself, Rank 7 had delivered an</i>
 <i>extrodinary weapon to Rank 6.</i>

00:21:45.953 --> 00:21:47.855 position:5% line:83% align:start
So you brought a gun to this
fight?

00:21:48.355 --> 00:21:50.357 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Then I've got a little something</i>
 <i>for you!</i>

00:21:53.327 --> 00:21:58.366 position:5% line:77% align:start
(NARRATOR) <i>The anti-terraformar</i>
 <i>shindo-shiki-ninja sword! Known</i>
 <i>as...</i>

